{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704840/extras/7gJe+S.png?t=1724259998\" /><br><br>After dying, poisoned for unknown reasons, Isobel finds herself in the afterlife... and on a dangerous mission. Experience a truly unique visual novel full of character, mystery and heart as you point and click your way to unveiling the strange world of Purgatory's many secrets.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704840/extras/zVcWLz.png?t=1724259998\" /> <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704840/extras/lwzqQa.png?t=1724259998\" /> <strong>Enter</strong> a truly memorable story told in four acts, full of choices and branching outcomes both big and small.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704840/extras/lwzqQa.png?t=1724259998\" /> <strong>Explore</strong> the interactive world of Purgatory through a day-night cycle with four segments per day... lots of stuff to click on (or not, if you don't want to).<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704840/extras/lwzqQa.png?t=1724259998\" /> <strong>Meet</strong> unforgettable characters, all with their own fleshed out personalities and agendas, brought to life by partial voice acting.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704840/extras/lwzqQa.png?t=1724259998\" /> <strong>Stay</strong> connected to the Dwellers and Denizens of the afterlife via the PurgaPhone! Send and receive messages, with many of them unique to the choices you make.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704840/extras/lwzqQa.png?t=1724259998\" /> <strong>Partake</strong> in nine different character routes, as well as a number of exciting side stories that further develop the world, and watch as their outcomes change the main narrative in meaningful ways.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704840/extras/lwzqQa.png?t=1724259998\" /> <strong>Marvel</strong> at sprites, backgrounds, special scenes and inventory items all drawn in a beautiful and unique style.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704840/extras/lwzqQa.png?t=1724259998\" /> <strong>Unlock</strong> a wealth of hidden treasures, such as gallery images, music tracks and encyclopedia entries.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704840/extras/lwzqQa.png?t=1724259998\" /> <strong>Bop</strong> your head to a dynamic soundtrack composed by popular YouTube artist Endigo.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704840/extras/pQFG50.png?t=1724259998\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704840/extras/isobelbio.png?t=1724259998\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704840/extras/blissbio.png?t=1724259998\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704840/extras/sheolbio.png?t=1724259998\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704840/extras/apechsbio.png?t=1724259998\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704840/extras/remmbio.png?t=1724259998\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704840/extras/volbio.png?t=1724259998\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.ste